    DestinationSearch --> ShowDestination: User input for name
    ShowDestination: 1. ChangeContact \n2. ChangeEmergencyNumber
    ShowDestination --> ChangeContact: Krafa 20
    ShowDestination --> ChangeEmergencyNumber: Krafa 21

}

